data.description: Absolutely adorable, immaculately maintained home offering vintage charm with all of the modern bells & whistles! Updated kitchen with granite countertops, butcher block island, custom tile backsplash, spacious pantry and a porcelain sink. Gorgeous red oak hard wood floors with inlay. New roof and gutters (Nov 22) and a Carrier HVAC split system. The back yard is fully fenced and comes with an oversized detached shed (as is). Catch a sunrise over the Hampton Roads Harbor only 1 block away or launch your boat at the public boat ramp just minutes from your door!Seller will consider paying a portion of buyer's closing costs with an acceptable offer.
